B.a7r=new A.j0("gym-tracker","GYM Workout","Personal Fitness Companion App","A full-featured personal fitness tracker built with Flutter & Dart. Managing your fitness journey shouldn't be complicated \u2014 this app brings everything you need into one clean, easy-to-use interface.\n\nWorkout Scheduling \u2014 Create and manage multiple workout schedules with custom exercises, sets, and reps.\n\nLive Workout Tracking \u2014 Log daily workouts in real time, track start/end times and exercise completion.\n\nQuick Stats & Insights \u2014 Visual charts showing workout frequency, current streak, weekly goal progress, and muscle group breakdown.\n\nWeight Tracker \u2014 Log your weight over time with a visual progress chart.\n\nHealth Dashboard \u2014 Track BMI, calculate daily calorie needs (TDEE), and get personalized macro breakdowns (protein, carbs, fat) based on your body stats and goals using the Mifflin-St Jeor Equation.\n\nGoogle Sign-In \u2014 Secure OAuth authentication with a personalized welcome experience.\n\nFully offline \u2014 all data is stored locally on-device using SQLite.",B.a0d,B.cQ,B.R2,B.VD)
